title: Breadcrumb Nav
description: a navigation container for breadcrumb trail links
nhsuk: https://service-manual.nhs.uk/design-system/components/breadcrumbs
---

{% from "components/breadcrumb-nav/macro.njk" import breadcrumbNav %}
{% from "components/breadcrumb-list/macro.njk" import breadcrumbList %}
{% from "components/breadcrumb-list-item/macro.njk" import breadcrumbListItem %}
{% from "components/breadcrumb-link/macro.njk" import breadcrumbLink %}

<h2>Default</h2>
<p>The breadcrumb family composes four macros: <code>BreadcrumbNav</code>,
  <code>BreadcrumbList</code>, <code>BreadcrumbListItem</code>, and
  <code>BreadcrumbLink</code>. Mark the current page by passing
  <code>current: true</code> to its list item.</p>

{% call breadcrumbNav() %}
  {% call breadcrumbList() %}
    {% call breadcrumbListItem() %}
      {{ breadcrumbLink({ href: "/", text: "Home" }) }}
    {% endcall %}
    {% call breadcrumbListItem() %}
      {{ breadcrumbLink({ href: "/health-a-z/", text: "Health A to Z" }) }}
    {% endcall %}
    {{ breadcrumbListItem({ text: "Flu", current: true }) }}
  {% endcall %}
{% endcall %}

<h2>With custom aria-label</h2>
{% call breadcrumbNav({ label: "You are here" }) %}
  {% call breadcrumbList() %}
    {% call breadcrumbListItem() %}
      {{ breadcrumbLink({ href: "/", text: "NHS home" }) }}
    {% endcall %}
    {{ breadcrumbListItem({ text: "Services", current: true }) }}
  {% endcall %}
{% endcall %}
